short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: create call logs from google sheets notes

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
This extension is to be used with NGP VAN to assist with creating call logs.

It will take the data from your google sheets file and auto fill name and notes it appropriate field.

For more information on how to use the extension as well as how to format the google sheets file refer to the following resources:

 Format google sheets: Covers removing duplicates, characters, and combining cells

https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=I_Q859YJ_Ss&t=4s
